data.description: BACK ON MARKET!  Lower Price Too! FOR SALE Modeled Home in Oakridge @ McSweeney Farms.  Has 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms.  Two Bedrooms and two bathrooms downstairs. Master Bedroom and Master Bathroom are on main floor including the Laundry room.  Three bedrooms and one bath upstairs.  There's also a loft upstairs for game room or another family room area.  Home has vaulted ceilings with faux wood beams. Classic smoke shaker style cabinets and quartz counters with full height backsplash. Large breakfast bar island by the kitchen. It's in the Diamond Valley area of the master planned community of McSweeny Farms with large recreation building including gym/fitness center, pool, spa,and party facilities. HOME has a SOLAR (Leased).  A MUST SEE!!  NEGOTIABLE.. Thank you..
